Uses of Class
com.revature.model.Employee

  • Packages that use Employee 
    Package Description
    com.revature.controller
    Provides the controller classes which are used to establish end-points for all HTTP requests to the Training Service
    com.revature.model
    Provides the model classes which are used to represent data for Revature batches, employees, and associates.
    com.revature.repo
    Provides the repository classes which are used to interact with the database to retrieve and store information related to Revature batches, and their corresponding employees and associates.
    com.revature.service
    Provides the service interfaces and classes which implement methods related to Revature batches, and their corresponding employees and associates.
